      <div class="cs-body-text">
        <p>I created multiple iterations of the user flows, taking into account the feedback we had received from the team and making sure that the user flow was intuitive and easy to follow. To ensure that the user flow was efficient, I also eliminated any unnecessary steps and simplified the design wherever possible. I worked closely with the developers to make sure that the design was feasible and that the developers had a clear understanding of what needed to be built.</p>
